    name: "Sarah L",
    role: "Family Law Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/laptop-notebook-work-hand-suit-people-1278242-pxhere.com_.jpg",
  },
  {
    logo: "BRAND LOGO",
    quote:
      "After a serious accident, I felt overwhelmed. They took over the fight and secured a settlement that changed my family's .",
    name: "David K",
    role: "Corporate Law Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/person-people-girl-woman-hair-white-642888-pxhere.com_11zon-scaled-1.jpg",
  },
  {
    logo: "BRAND LOGO",
    quote:
      "Their strategic approach to our complex merger saved us months of negotiation. They are more than just lawyers; they are .",
    name: "Michael R",
    role: "Personal Injury Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/man-person-people-hair-white-boy-1046502-pxhere.com_.jpg",
  },
  {
    logo: "BRAND LOGO",
    quote:
      "They handled my estate planning with clarity, patience, and professionalism.",
    name: "Anna P",
    role: "Estate Planning Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/person-people-girl-woman-hair-white-642888-pxhere.com_11zon-scaled-1.jpg",
  },
  {
    logo: "BRAND LOGO",
    quote:
      "Their communication was consistent and honest. I always knew exactly.",
    name: "Robert M",
    role: "Real Estate Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/laptop-notebook-work-hand-suit-people-1278242-pxhere.com_.jpg",
  },
  {
    logo: "BRAND LOGO",
    quote:
      "Their communication was consistent and honest. I always knew exactly.",
    name: "Robert M",
    role: "Real Estate Client",
    image:
      "https://civitas.divigurus.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/laptop-notebook-work-hand-suit-people-1278242-pxhere.com_.jpg",
